<p>i was looking at your site and thought i'd share with you the way i lace my
boots. My boots stay tight and feel good (well to me they do.) I just square
knot at the top and tuck the rest into the boot.</p>
<p>Loopy Ladder Lacing:</p>
<pre>
outside  inside

 O--O
 O  O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
 |  |
 O  O     O==O
</pre>
