<pre>
outside   inside
-------   -------
 o--o      o o
            \ |
 o--o      o o
            \ |
 o--o      o o
            \ |
 o--o      o o
          |   |
-o  o-     o o
</pre>
the one side is just looped straight out the end, while the other side of the
lace does all the work... ofcourse the diagonals would go the other way on the
other shoe.
