<p>notice the nice italian leather used in sneakers.. even italian nikes use
this look and material.</p>
<p>i think mine may have come this way - maybe not.. i still think my shoes are
laced cooler.</p>
<pre>
outside   inside
-------   -------
 o--o      o o(a)
            \
 o--o      o o
            \
 o--o      o o   (does this shoe appear crooked on your terminal too?)
            \
 o--o      o o
            \
-o  o-  (b)o o
</pre>
<p>the other end of the (inner) lace connects a to b, running visible the whole
way up.</p>
